<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <style>
        .mail-container{
            width: 100vw;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px solid lightgray;
        }
        .header{
            width: 100%;
            height: 50px ;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-family: monospace;
            text-align: center;
            color: #1f4d91;
        }
        .message-box{
            font-family: cursive;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-top: 5px; 
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .email-content{
            width: 98%;
            padding: 5%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-family: monospace;
            color: #828283;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    
<div class="mail-container">
    <div class="header">
        <a><h1>OTP Verfication</h1></a>
    </div>

    <br><br>
    <div class="email-content">
        Hello, <br><br>

Your OTP: " <%= otp%> " .

Enter it on the verification page.<br>

If not you? Ignore.
<br><br>
Stripe Team
    </div>
</div>
    
</body>
</html>
